        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 44–61. Anaceratagallia (Anaceratagallia) venosa, calling signal oscillograms. Faster oscillograms of the parts of signals indicated as “53–60” are given under the same numbers. 44–45, 53―males from Crimea, locality No. 1 in the list in call- ing signal description, 46, 54―male from Rostov Oblast, ibid., locality No. 2, 47, 55―male from Kokpek Ravine, Kazakhstan, ibid., locality No. 3, 48–49, 56―male from Altynemel, Kazakhstan, ibid., locality No. 4, 50–51, 57–59―males from Sarkand, Kazakhstan, ibid., locality No. 5, 52, 60–61―male from Altai Mts., ibid., locality No. 6." ;
